        "Description": "To: Gregory Arthur\rFrom: Dawood Rangan\r\rMr. Artuhur,\r\rToday we will be shooting the climax of Mumbai Hero, the protagonist&apos;s all-out assault on the witch and her headquarters. Remember to wear your costume this time and that the script calls for the villainous witch to be killed in an explosion. This is the second most important scene in my great movie. Mess it up and you are fired!\r\rSincerely,\r\rDawood Rangan",
